        <div class='cta-button-small'>
          <a href='/#signup' class='button-secondary'>Sign up</a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main>
        <div class="careers-content">
          <h1>Careers at lnksbot</h1>
          
          <p>Join our team and help build the future of content discovery and knowledge management. At lnksbot, we're on a mission to transform how people collect, process, and consume online content.</p>
          
          <h2>Our Values</h2>
          
          <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
              <h3>User-Centered Innovation</h3>
              <p>We put our users at the center of everything we build, constantly seeking feedback and iterating to create experiences that truly solve problems.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="value-card">
              <h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
              <p>We embrace a growth mindset, constantly learning and improving our skills, our product, and our understanding of user needs.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="value-card">
              <h3>Transparent Communication</h3>
              <p>We believe in open, honest communication within our team and with our users, sharing both successes and challenges.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="value-card">
              <h3>Responsible AI</h3>
              <p>We develop AI systems with a focus on fairness, transparency, and user control, ensuring our technology serves human needs ethically.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <h2>Benefits</h2>
          
          <p>We offer competitive compensation, flexible work arrangements, comprehensive health benefits, and a supportive, inclusive work environment. We believe in work-life balance and provide generous paid time off, parental leave, and professional development opportunities.</p>
          
