            <p>Join our AI team to develop and improve our content analysis and summarization algorithms. You'll work with large language models, natural language processing, and machine learning techniques to extract insights from diverse content sources.</p>
            <a href="#" class="apply-button">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
          
