              </span>
            </div>
            <p>We're seeking a talented product designer to create beautiful, intuitive interfaces for our web and mobile applications. You'll collaborate with our product and engineering teams to design experiences that make complex information accessible and engaging.</p>
            <a href="#" class="apply-button">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
          
          <p>Don't see a position that matches your skills? We're always interested in meeting talented people. Send your resume to <a href="mailto:careers@lnksbot.com">careers@lnksbot.com</a> with a note about how you could contribute to our team.</p>
